This directory vendors Mermaid as a single self-contained browser bundle:

    vendor/mermaid.min.js  —  Mermaid v11.15.0  (UMD build, ~3.2 MB)
    Source:  https://www.npmjs.com/package/mermaid  (https://github.com/mermaid-js/mermaid)

It is redistributed unmodified under the MIT License, reproduced in full below per its terms. The
live viewer (`bun run serve`) serves this file to the browser to render ```mermaid diagram blocks
offline; it is a vendored static asset, not a runtime dependency of the server.

